3:T424,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ProfessionalService","name":"Creative Production | I am Tomas","description":"Commercial spots, image videos, and campaigns tailored to your brand.","image":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/images/service-creative.jpg","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/services/creative-production","telephone":"+420735846329","email":"msg@jajsemtomas.cz","priceRange":"££","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"London","addressCountry":"UK"},"provider":{"@type":"Person","name":"Tomas Berka","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz","jobTitle":"Video Producer & Filmmaker"},"areaServed":["London","United Kingdom","Europe"],"hasOfferCatalog":{"@type":"OfferCatalog","name":"Video Services","itemListElement":[{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Creative Concept"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Full-service Production"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"High-end Equipment"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Color Grading"}}]}}5:T92d,<h2>Video That Builds Brands</h2><p>Every company says they're 'different'. But how many actually <strong>show it</strong>? Creative video production isn't about pretty shots — it's about telling your brand story in a way that <strong>makes customers act</strong>.</p><h3>What I Create</h3><ul><li><strong>Commercial spots</strong> — TV ads, online pre-roll, YouTube ads. From 15-second bumpers to 60-second brand stories</li><li><strong>Brand films</strong> — Your company's business card. For websites, investors, internal comms. Cinematic quality</li><li><strong>Product videos</strong> — Professional product presentation, unboxing, demos. E-commerce conversions go up</li><li><strong>Campaign series</strong> — Consistent visual style across entire campaigns. From concept to final delivery</li></ul><h3>Why Me</h3><p>I'm not just a 'guy with a camera'. I started as an actor and presenter — I understand working with people on camera. I think like a <strong>marketer</strong>: every shot has a reason, every cut guides the viewer toward conversion. I've worked with DEKRA, Roklen24, WikyHračky, and dozens of other companies across Europe.</p><h3>How It Works</h3><ol><li><strong>Initial brief</strong> — I understand your goal, target audience, and budget</li><li><strong>Concept & storyboard</strong> — I present creative solutions, you approve the script</li><li><strong>Pre-production</strong> — Locations, casting, equipment, schedule. I handle everything</li><li><strong>Shooting</strong> — Professional crew, cinematic lighting, quality audio</li><li><strong>Post-production</strong> — Editing, color grading, graphics, music, sound design</li><li><strong>Delivery</strong> — Final video in all formats + 2 rounds of revisions included</li></ol><h3>Indicative Pricing</h3><p><strong>Product video:</strong> from €600 — 1 shooting day, basic post-production</p><p><strong>Brand / image video:</strong> from €1,400 — Concept, shooting, cinematic post-production</p><p><strong>Commercial spot:</strong> from €2,000 — Full production including talent and locations</p><p><strong>Campaign package:</strong> Custom quote — Multiple videos, consistent visual identity</p><p><em>Final price depends on project scope. <a href='/contact'>Send your brief</a> — you'll have a quote within 48 hours.</em></p>0:{"buildId":"Z9swWMs31Un3nKsGRJucP","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"py-20","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"items":[{"name":"Home","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz"},{"name":"Services","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/#services"},{"name":"Creative Production","url":"https://en.jajsemtomas.cz/services/creative-production"}]}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$3"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much does a commercial spot cost?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"It depends on the scope of the project. Basic spot from £950, complex production with actors and locations from £1,800. I'll always give you the price upfront.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How long does production take?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"From the first call to the final video usually 2-4 weeks. It depends on the complexity of the project.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do you provide actors and locations?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, I can provide complete production including casting, locations, and equipment.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can you film a TV commercial?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, for large projects I collaborate with SocialVids, who have experience with TV commercials.\"}}]}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8","children":[["$","$L4",null,{"href":"/#services","className":"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary mb-8 transition-colors","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left h-4 w-4 mr-2","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}]," Back to services"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6","children":"Creative Production"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 text-pretty","children":"Commercial spots, image videos, and campaigns tailored to your brand."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-p:text-muted-foreground prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-strong:text-foreground mb-8 text-base","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$5"}}],"$L6","$undefined"]}],"$L7"]}],"$L8","$L9"]}]]}],["$La"],"$Lb"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
